1) Set desired WORKDIR in script.sh
2) Run script in Ubuntu using
```
sudo ./script.sh
```

NOTE: The board should be in recovery mode and connected to the host PC for the purpose of this test.

Steps in these script were automated based on the instructions available at https://docs.nvidia.com/jetson/archives/r35.3.1/DeveloperGuide/text/SD/SoftwarePackagesAndTheUpdateMechanism.html#preparing-for-an-image-based-ota-update
